--- step [B] ---
Create partitions using cfdisk:

Partitions to create
-------------------------------
| EFI    |  fat32 |  512MiB   |
| root   |  ext4  |  custom   |
| swap   |  swap  |  ram size |
-------------------------------

Format partitions:

mkfs.fat -F32 /dev/sda1    # EFI
mkfs.ext4 /dev/sda2        # root
mkswap /dev/sda3           # swap
swapon /dev/sda3

Next step: [C]